Package: mason.github
Title: GitHub R Package Generator for Mason
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <csardi.gabor@gmail.com>
Description: A Mason template for an R package that
    is developed at GitHub. It includes configuration,
    files for continuous integration, badges for CIs and CRAN versions,
    README files, a NEWS file.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/mason.github
BugReports: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/mason.github/issues
Imports:
    ask,
    httr,
    falsy,
    whoami
Remotes:
    metacran/mason
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
